<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08859</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT REQUIRING GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS IN CHARGE OF PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION TO RIDE PUBLIC TRANSPORT AT LEAST ONCE A MONTH</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to address Metro Manila's lack of efficient mass transit system serving millions of Filipinos
living and working in the area.

Proposes to stir up empathy among concerned government officials to have first-hand experience riding public transportation to determine how to resolve the issue.
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>CASTELO, WINSTON &quot;WINNIE&quot;</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-01-21</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRANSPORTATION ON 2019-01-23</td></tr></table>